WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.489 --> 00:00:02.997
The process for non expendable equipment

2
00:00:02.997 --> 00:00:06.108
begins with the equipment committee, or EC.

3
00:00:06.108 --> 00:00:08.415
This teams has the responsibility

4
00:00:08.415 --> 00:00:10.528
to approve equipment purchases

5
00:00:10.528 --> 00:00:12.674
and consists of stakeholders that are charged

6
00:00:12.674 --> 00:00:15.807
with ensuring that facility requirements

7
00:00:15.807 --> 00:00:18.014
are valid and approved as needed.

8
00:00:18.014 --> 00:00:22.651
Requests that are above $3,500 go to Network Contracting.

9
00:00:22.651 --> 00:00:25.369
Those that are at or under $3,500

10
00:00:25.369 --> 00:00:28.154
go to the logistics inventory manager

11
00:00:28.154 --> 00:00:30.107
and a purchase card is used.

12
00:00:30.107 --> 00:00:31.815
Select each checklist item

13
00:00:31.815 --> 00:00:33.458
to step through this process

14
00:00:33.458 --> 00:00:35.762
as it applies to non expendable equipment.

